Package com.codingchallenge.workload

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TestingSecurityManager
    A special implementation of SecurityManager that throws a RuntimeException when System#exit(int) is called.
    Workload
    Workload is the base class for processing arrays and returning appropriate String if the array is arranged in wave pattern or if it is not.
    WorkloadApp
    WorkloadApp contains main method and represents the entry point of this program.
    WorkloadAppTest
    WorkloadAppTest is a unit test for WorkloadApp class.
    WorkloadTest
    WorkloadTest is a test for Workload class.
    WorkloadWithTestsIT
    Integration test for the WorkloadApp program.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TestingSecurityManager.TestExitException
    An exception that stores the exit code for later verification.
